title: Something unexpected happened creating lobby
body:
Hi,

Just requesting for help or info on this error, first time getting it and when I searched most forums were from last year so wondering if this is just me right now and how do I resolve this issue.

replies.body:
Seems like Riot was able to get a fix rolled out. Let us know if you're still encountering any issues!

> [{quoted}](name=Agent Mindstar,realm=OCE,application-id=ElA0rvVL,discussion-id=9OpzaJih,comment-id=0003,timestamp=2018-06-12T00:52:45.251+0000)
>
> Everything should be fixed now.
> 
> The cause was a backend update which caused lobby creation to break - meaning nobody could get in game.  We've rolled it back and it should all be smooth sailing now.  
> 
> Sorry for the interruption to your morning games.
> 
> Cheers
> Mindstar



https://boards.oce.leagueoflegends.com/en/c/help-support-oce/9OpzaJih-something-went-wrong?comment=0003
